            <string>&lt;b&gt;Input Simulation Tool&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;Method for typing transcribed text.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;XDOTOOL:&lt;/b&gt; Simulates X11 keyboard events&lt;br&gt;- More compatible with all applications&lt;br&gt;- Requires xdotool installed&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;DOTOOL:&lt;/b&gt; Uses /dev/uinput directly&lt;br&gt;- Faster and more reliable&lt;br&gt;- Requires root or udev configuration</string>
